# detroit.dev — AI provider configuration
# Copy to .env and fill in whichever provider(s) you want.
# For local development: just run Ollama (no key needed).
# For Vercel deployment: set these in the Vercel dashboard, NOT here.

# Groq (free tier — https://console.groq.com)
# GROQ_API_KEY=gsk_...

# NVIDIA (free tier — https://build.nvidia.com)
# NVIDIA_API_KEY=nvapi-...

# OpenRouter (many models — https://openrouter.ai)
# OPENROUTER_API_KEY=sk-or-...

# OpenAI
# OPENAI_API_KEY=sk-...

# Or just run Ollama locally (no key needed):
#   ollama pull nemotron-mini
#   python tools/serve.py
